tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE telehealth_studies (
    study_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    study_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    study_description TEXT,
    start_date DATE,
    end_date DATE,
    patient_id INT,
    patient_gender CHAR(1),
    patient_age INT,
    patient_condition VARCHAR(255),
    data_collected BOOLEAN
);

CREATE TABLE Patients (
  patient_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  patient_name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
  age INT,
  gender VARCHAR(10),
  medical_history TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE StudyResults (
  result_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  study_id INT,
  patient_id INT,
  study_date DATE,
  result_description TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE research_studies (
    study_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    study_name VARCHAR(100),
    study_description TEXT,
    start_date DATE,
    end_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE clinical_trials (
    trial_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    trial_name VARCHAR(100),
    trial_description TEXT,
    start_date DATE,
    end_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE telehealth_research_studies (study_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
study_name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
start_date DATE,
end_date DATE,
lead_researcher VARCHAR(100));

CREATE TABLE clinical_trials (trial_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
trial_name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
start_date DATE,
end_date DATE,
principal_investigator VARCHAR(100));

CREATE TABLE patient_data (patient_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
patient_name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
age INT,
gender VARCHAR(10),
diagnosis TEXT,
study_id INT REFERENCES telehealth_research_studies(study_id),
trial_id INT REFERENCES clinical_trials(trial_id));

CREATE TABLE data_analysis (analysis_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
study_id INT REFERENCES telehealth_research_studies(study_id),
trial_id INT REFERENCES clinical_trials(trial_id),
analysis_date DATE,
findings TEXT);

CREATE TABLE patients (
  patient_id INT NOT NULL,
  patient_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
  patient_age INT,
  study_id INT NOT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (patient_id),
  FOREIGN KEY (study_id) REFERENCES studies(study_id)
);

CREATE TABLE visits (
  visit_id INT NOT NULL,
  patient_id INT NOT NULL,
  visit_date DATE NOT NULL,
  visit_type VARCHAR(50),
  PRIMARY KEY (visit_id),
  FOREIGN KEY (patient_id) REFERENCES patients(patient_id)
);

CREATE TABLE measurements (
  measurement_id INT NOT NULL,
  visit_id INT NOT NULL,
  measurement_type VARCHAR(50),
  value DECIMAL,
  PRIMARY KEY (measurement_id),
  FOREIGN KEY (visit_id) REFERENCES visits(visit_id)
);
